import React from 'react'
import { Button, Card, CardActions, CardContent, Typography, Grid } from '@material-ui/core'

const MyCard = () => {
    return (
        <Card>
            <CardContent>
                <Grid container>
                    <Grid item>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>

            </CardContent>
            <CardActions>
                <Button variant="outlined" color="primary">
                    Show Detail
                </Button>
                <Button variant="outlined" color="primary">
                    {new Date().toString()}
                </Button>
            </CardActions>
        </Card>
    )
}
export default MyCard
